    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p> Disabled Military Child Protection Act of 2013 - Authorizes monthly annuity payments under the Survivor Benefit Plan (SBP) to a supplemental or special needs trust established for the sole benefit of a disabled dependent child who is incapable of self-support because of mental or physical incapacity.</p>]]></text>
